Package main.util.constants

Class SystemConfigConstants

java.lang.Object
main.util.constants.SystemConfigConstants
public class SystemConfigConstants
extends java.lang.Object
This class provides the constants for the entire system. Contains networking IPs and ports for UDP packets and sockets.
Author:
Tony Zeidan, Evan Lloyd, Shaopeng Liu, Leenesh Kumar, YouHeng Zhou, Dominic Motora
